:::Starscream/Bludgeon/Obsidian/Sharpedge/Godfather/Depth Charge:::

::Starscream, Bludgeon and Obsidian walk into the mess hall and see Drillbit 
with a glass of energin::
Bludgeon: Hmm, i think theres something wrong here.
Obsidian: agreed, our leader looks a little down.
Starscream: Well, lets talk to him, find out whats the problem. Hey Drillbit 
is anything wrong?
~~~~~
::Sharpedge and Godfather land at the CF, and see that the Maximals and 
Alliance(mostly) werent firing on each other. They walked up to Shockaract::
Sharpedge: Whats going on here Shockaract?
~~~~~
::Depth Charge was flying all around the planet, just trying to get his head 
straight.  The battle that was currently happening seemed over, but he knew 
that was far from the truth.  Battles never really end, has he had learned. 
Both he and Protoform X are still alive, even after their brutal battle at 
the end of the Beast Wars. He decided he needed to do something drastic. He 
opened up a comm to Rampage::
Depth Charge: Hey X, this is Depth Charge. Thats right, im alive. Id be 
willing to finish this long rivalry, if you come to my position. What do you 
say?

--part1_fb.108f6154.279cb0e8_boundary
